      "body" : "Note: a potential use-case of <code>&amp;=</code> is if you are iterating through a for loop with a &quot;result&quot; variable set to true by default, and wanted to set it to false if at any point during the for loop what you are evaluating is false, while also preventing it from being reset back to true once it is false for the first time."
